We all suffer from lupus and it’s a debilitating disease. Most ppl don’t even know what Lupus is so if you can take one minute out of your day today and just read a fact about Lupus. It’s an autoimmune disease that that cause the body to attack itself. It comes in different forms and causes complications that are deadly. If you know someone who has lupus be patient with them, love on them, most importantly pray for them because we fight a battle every single day just to get out of bed.#worldlupusday2023🦋🎗️💜✝️🦋🎗️💜✝️#lupuswarrior💜🦋
